%sql
-- find the most active member
SELECT members.member_id, members.member_name, count(rsvps.rsvp_id) as num_rsvp FROM members JOIN rsvps ON rsvps.member_id = members.member_id GROUP BY members.member_id, members.member_name ORDER BY num_rsvp DESC LIMIT 20

%sql
-- find the most popular group (people answer 'rsvp = yes')
SELECT groups.group_id, groups.group_name, groups.group_urlname, count(rsvps.rsvp_id) as rsvp_yes FROM groups JOIN rsvps ON groups.group_id = rsvps.group_id WHERE rsvps.response = 'yes' GROUP BY groups.group_id, groups.group_name, groups.group_urlname ORDER BY rsvp_yes DESC LIMIT 20
